Jaws:





Jaws swam around in the water near his pod as his memory circuits activated.  
Most of them were damaged.  He knew his name, and what a Cybertronian was and 
how to transform, but he didn't know what side he was on, if any.

"Jaws...transform!" he yelled, his body twisting and converting into the 
shape of a biped.  He treated in the water, the large great white shark 
staying in the same place, the blade-like dorsal fins on his elbows splashing 
water.
